\f2\i0 \cf2 A Primer on the Divine Order of the Spirit in the Church\
\
The Acts 15 Cosmologica-Pneumatic Key Frame describes a theological framework rooted in the Jerusalem Council of Acts 15, where the apostles discerned the Spirit\'92s activity among the Gentiles. This moment reveals a cosmological order for the inclusion of the nations into the covenant of grace, establishing a pattern of spiritual discernment, authority, and unity under the Word of God.\
\
This key frame bridges the Old Testament prophetic promises with the New Covenant reality in Christ by using pneumatology (the study of the Holy Spirit) to reveal divine governance within the Church. It models a spiritual geometry where law, grace, and prophecy meet in a cosmic balance of truth and mercy.\
\
