VIII. Theological Significance of the Acts 15 Key Frame\
\
The Acts 15 Cosmologica-Pneumatic Key Frame serves as a spiritual blueprint for:\
	\'95	Unity in Diversity: One Spirit, multiple cultures.\
	\'95	Freedom with Form: The Spirit works within divine order.\
	\'95	Prophetic Fulfillment: The Old Testament is fulfilled, not abolished.\
\
This Key Frame reminds the Church that:\
	\'95	God\'92s order is eternal.\
	\'95	The Spirit\'92s work continues.\
	\'95	Christ\'92s reign is now.\
